<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Access&nbsp;SCiPNET&nbsp;Email?&nbsp;One&nbsp;(1)&nbsp;new&nbsp;message!</a></div>
